story_txt:
ChangeWe are in a desperate need of it.Whether we talk about society, politics, economy or digital divide. Have you felt at least once that the world goes wrong? How often have you seen your friends or family complaining of the "current state of affairs"?Bulgaria is the poorest, least developed and likewise most corrupted country in the European Union. We, as Europeans have the freedom to work and live everywhere in the EU. Yet we choose to live in Bulgaria. We believe that even the poorest country in the EU deserves to be a prospering place to live in.To achieve that, we will have to effect some changes. To kickstart the change, though, we have to spring into action and participate in politics.  TogetherWe started establishing DEOS, a political party of a new type. Now you might be wondering who we are and this is perfectly fine.  We are a group of concerned Bulgarians who are saying "enough". We believe the change potential sits within every one of us.What will we do to initiate change:

We are developing a model to shake up the basics of political representation. We believe in empowering people to actively participate in political decisions;


Our model will transform the political parties from the power brokers of today to the transparent opinion builders and opinion leaders of tomorrow;


Bulgaria is not governed by rules, but by deals and corruption instead. We will work to complete the transition from arbitrary deal making towards a predictive rule of law;


Education forms the foundation of our children's future. Today it is done all wrong. Empowering active parents and kids to decide on their education formats is a key change we aim to achieve

Reach outWe need your help. The applicable legislation provides for a long, tedious and expensive process of establishing a political party.We initiate our indiegogo campaign to:

reach to our fellow Bulgarians home and abroad, who dream of a change and are willing to make it happen - online and on site


finance the initial general assembly gathering of DEOS


further develop the model of political change we as founders of DEOS envision

We call for the support of all of you, Bulgarians or not, living in Bulgaria, European countries, USA, Canada or elsewhere. Help us change Bulgaria! Our success could be the role-model to change the world!
